- Cross-feature persisted state uses `atomWithStorage` in `src/state`.
- Derivations use `atom(get => ...)`, write-only use `atom(null, (get, set, arg) => ...)`.
- Use feature components/hooks to read/write with `useAtom`/`useSetAtom`.
